{"tid":218981,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人寫essay好慢","createTime":"2017-04-27T01:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T05:19:58.000Z","uid":41356,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c08d489427f701612851dd6ba403c8891410aae1","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"講緊千二字嘅essay要寫十幾二十個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n寫篇文用最多時間就係用google scholar, 淨係睇extract都用撚曬啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當每一段有2個sub point, 每個subpoint由背景資料到影響都要落citation, 一個簡單推論可能要落四五個citation, 成篇就廿幾三十個，好怕個tutor真係走去check篇論文講乜<br />\n<br />\n結果其他科無時間溫on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以作快啲<br />\n目標係十個鐘千二字"},{"pid":"48bbadb46aabda1c65a23201f7db45f978905603","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"推推佢"},{"pid":"abc71b44731dc60128a08b58a07543e393c958c3","tid":218981,"uid":73422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"hea 做"},{"pid":"3140b75d5f5ea23256a2006eee1e0abb3555c431","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hea 做</blockquote><br />\n喂有無啲積極啲嘅辦法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674d559100105d5b6a25ce74914bd6cb1b6c0406","tid":218981,"uid":6140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"Deadline 前十個鐘做"},{"pid":"d67ff0f591ee9dd8cb054e5032f3ea948946891d","tid":218981,"uid":77739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:08:19.000Z","msg":"千五字寫十幾廿日是常識吧"},{"pid":"2e70a9586d95dcd4e0d6ce68afd816008856af5e","tid":218981,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Deadline 前十個鐘做</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3a08cb066bb740966aca82164e8e18b66ef580","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Deadline 前十個鐘做</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌駁唔到<br />\n用呢個approach我可以一個鐘寫千二字添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之但係我唔想做deadline fighter呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2a31eae31175032fb4aa07a88f302c0b2ab53e","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講緊千二字嘅essay要寫十幾二十個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n寫篇文用最多時間就係用google scholar, 淨係睇extract都用撚曬啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當每一段有2個sub point, 每個subpoint由背景資料到影響都要落citation, 一個簡單推論可能要落四五個citation, 成篇就廿幾三十個，好怕個tutor真係走去check篇論文講乜<br />\n<br />\n結果其他科無時間溫on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以作快啲<br />\n目標係十個鐘千二字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌都未撚計搵啲同義字呀，生字嘅usage嘅時間<br />\n睇下例句咁又加多幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abff12a474cd102fa21f092dfdbad9ee4648d17","tid":218981,"uid":30859,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n專心唔撚到<br />\n屌<br />\n訓幾個鐘繼續<br />\n屌屌屌屌屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f09e34b3f3fd7a49be50cd6622fe016b5979e78","tid":218981,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"因為時間多，咪寫得細緻啲，咁自然就慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63dc99557d041d7f9f7b45e6fbe4e55b525c06e","tid":218981,"uid":22643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"十幾個鐘都叫慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820f4e3ed8caca5269daa7a5966d62345a079e04","tid":218981,"uid":34764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />組織能力極差<br />\n睇hkeaa作文5**考生示例 唔明佢地點係兩個鐘寫到篇咁高質既文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7872092b2f779196240155078362d07b5b384bb7","tid":218981,"uid":35384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"寫一個禮拜...<br />\n仲要寫唔到啲咩出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下點樣可以寫得長啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4922d75396857e501b0fbea59cc4f447147ecf","tid":218981,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"十個鐘算快啦"},{"pid":"2a067ec7c359b2ecacf9d397bb5b0d65e2a16619","tid":218981,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"唔算好慢"},{"pid":"62a58d76f997551aa6fdf31d3eaa11854c3178ea","tid":218981,"uid":59659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"寫前plan好晒每段寫咩寫幾多，見咁上下就下段，快好多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91886a1ef3a5aa66ee008b0e013dbe20db5affaa","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十幾個鐘都叫慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廿個鐘攤開幾日嚟寫呀<br />\n<br />\n你幾日唔通連寫72個鐘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9795f2b60e6a2de392ed487a2d94ab03286f1422","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔算好慢</blockquote><br />\n[緊急] 趕essay 求救<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/218530?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/218530?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔係喎，隔離post啲人話四個鐘都寫得完<br />\n如果我四個鐘寫得完是但一篇essay, 其他科應該可以高半個龜"},{"pid":"3f2429d4c61e05e07120deb1ed763dadcc315276","tid":218981,"uid":47021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"二千字左右要十幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵ref同整結構用十個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6923d95223fcbd0615f7ea44b303051739dd9dd","tid":218981,"uid":91389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:58:13.000Z","msg":"我英文差，以前做essay前，睇書都睇十幾日，寫又hea + chur寫十幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae5fbdbe77b7d4b2e4a788f85faa068e1d48ef2","tid":218981,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"我，唔明D人點解可以寫咁多野出黎"},{"pid":"6d1c8da1879704eb35fc4c64f4b5d9ce5b69ce39","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我，唔明D人點解可以寫咁多野出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫多又唔算太難，我習慣睇好多reading先落手寫，左cite右cite，跟住唔係論文嗰啲文章就偷下佢idea再rephrase, 搭住啲citation咁出<br />\n成日寫到爆字，又神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一敗筆係好撚慢"},{"pid":"a1c093958fb609937af93ad56911e86e76df85da","tid":218981,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我，唔明D人點解可以寫咁多野出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫多又唔算太難，我習慣睇好多reading先落手寫，左cite右cite，跟住唔係論文嗰啲文章就偷下佢idea再rephrase, 搭住啲citation咁出<br />\n成日寫到爆字，又神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一敗筆係好撚慢</blockquote><br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c68a2cf4568bce97beea699551175e273a917","tid":218981,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"外判"},{"pid":"88a1072fdef641832a73116aefde385142b59cbc","tid":218981,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"咩科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> econ 同 management essay都已經唔同啦"},{"pid":"3653935973f026c41fe3a3d8424d9d1cda0cd637","tid":218981,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n<br />\n利申：8個鐘寫3000字 最後A-<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e9438cf242203d281c2187bb826a11aa4157fa","tid":218981,"uid":54854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"屌同你一樣 我有時仲慢<br />\n不過自問大多數都好高質<br />\n我都好享受睇journal 推斷嘅過程"},{"pid":"beda87731793b1ba1dbcd76e782c9198f4584d0f","tid":218981,"uid":6132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"見到d law友24個鐘take home exam可以爆5000-7000字，覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92762e5a344fe1b8dfadbbffece7a736e6edcfe","tid":218981,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"都係寫得多就得"},{"pid":"136813aa26521c9599136582758d2bdde7901db2","tid":218981,"uid":70877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-