0字嘅essay你地幾耐做完?"},{"pid":"92eaed80e37dfb6a04c4e7cbeaa567af5922fbbe","tid":218981,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一份2000字嘅essay你地幾耐做完?</blockquote><br />\n好多睇D料難唔難搵。最難做試過2000字做比較。但真係搵晒都無人會比較兩者既分別"},{"pid":"2d4535c96ef58d8ac9256f203065845d1e515657","tid":218981,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我，唔明D人點解可以寫咁多野出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫多又唔算太難，我習慣睇好多reading先落手寫，左cite右cite，跟住唔係論文嗰啲文章就偷下佢idea再rephrase, 搭住啲citation咁出<br />\n成日寫到爆字，又神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯一敗筆係好撚慢</blockquote><br />\n問題係D Tutor 覺得係唔係OK。。"},{"pid":"ef37724dc7ebe06821451d066fc05bcfe184e5d0","tid":218981,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外判</blockquote><br />\n我都想搵人介紹邊度外判"},{"pid":"e453790e096af384fda278ad3468ee4fbe8ee0ba","tid":218981,"uid":66772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"搵ref都要幾日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea17fd50b8c2b90de72145acc0f9101a5ddc3b5b","tid":218981,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一份2000字嘅essay你地幾耐做完?</blockquote><br />\n好多睇D料難唔難搵。最難做試過2000字做比較。但真係搵晒都無人會比較兩者既分別</blockquote><br />\n試過一次<br />\n好熟同好認同搵返黎果份article<br />\nreview唔太多功夫<br />\ncitation寫到邊做到邊<br />\n通頂20粒鐘交貨straightA"},{"pid":"5ae8a340dda3ebbe80673370a204065a4f2013b5","tid":218981,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"寫咗一個星期了 先打得三百字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701403ca404eecae46f4bc636a4754af94f72642","tid":218981,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bl